parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The front end vibration can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition switch glitch can cause the vehicle to fail to start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.

symptoms: The engine dies or stalls while driving
the "Service Engine Soon" light comes on
the OBDII error code shows P0385 (Crankshaft Sensor B failed).
